一名[匿名用戶](http://logsoku.com/thread/hatsukari.2ch.net/news/1300377026/
"http://logsoku.com/thread/hatsukari.2ch.net/news/1300377026/")轉載名為《[白龍LEGEND](http://pr55.net/img/IMGe1MSOg.jpg
"http://pr55.net/img/IMGe1MSOg.jpg")》的[漫畫](http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E7%AB%9C_%28%E6%BC%AB%E7%94%BB%29
"http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BD%E7%AB%9C_\(%E6%BC%AB%E7%94%BB\)")內頁，這部作品由[天王寺大](http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E5%AF%BA%E5%A4%A7
"http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E5%AF%BA%E5%A4%A7")和[渡辺みちお](http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B8%A1%E8%BE%BA%E3%81%BF%E3%81%A1%E3%81%8A
"http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B8%A1%E8%BE%BA%E3%81%BF%E3%81%A1%E3%81%8A")創作，在地震之後[暫停發行](http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-03-17/hakuryu-
legend-manga-nuclear-power-themed-arc-dropped-from-mag
"http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-03-17/hakuryu-legend-manga-nuclear-
power-themed-arc-dropped-from-mag")；劇情講述一名記者調查「東東電力公司」，還預言會發生與車諾比輻射外洩事件同等級的核災。

